---

<MarketingLayout
  title="FastVideoCutter - The Fastest Online Video Trimmer"
  heroBadge="v2.0 Now Available"
  heroTitle='Trim Videos in <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-cyan-300">Seconds</span>, <br class="hidden md:block" /> Not Hours.'
  heroSubtitle="The fastest browser-based video cutter. No uploads, no quality loss, no watermarks. Edit your content instantly with our local processing engine."
  features={features}
>
  
  <!-- 針對首頁的 SEO 內容 (Below the fold) -->
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">Why use FastVideoCutter?</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6">
    Traditional online video editors force you to upload your large video files to their servers, which can take hours depending on your internet speed. 
    <strong>FastVideoCutter</strong> solves this problem by using advanced browser technologies (WebCodecs & WebAssembly) to process your video 
    directly on your device.
  </p>

  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">Key Benefits</h3>
  <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-gray-400 space-y-2">
    <li><strong>Zero Upload Time:</strong> Since files stay on your computer, editing starts immediately.</li>
    <li><strong>Security:</strong> Your personal or confidential footage is never exposed to the cloud.</li>
    <li><strong>High Performance:</strong> Utilizes your computer's GPU for smooth preview and fast rendering.</li>
  </ul>

  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">Supported Features</h3>
  <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-gray-400 space-y-2">
    <li>Video Trimming & Splitting</li>
    <li>Multi-track Editing (Video + Audio + Text)</li>
    <li>Add Background Music (MP3/WAV)</li>
    <li>Add Text & Subtitles with Custom Styles</li>
    <li>Volume Control & Audio Mixing</li>
  </ul>

</MarketingLayout>